{
  "page": "Lord of Cider Hall",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Lord of Cider Hall</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> was the title held by the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\">House Fossoway</a>, the ruler of <a href=\"/index.php/Cider_Hall\" title=\"Cider Hall\">Cider Hall</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Currently the Fossoways of Cider Hall are a house of <a href=\"/index.php/Landed_knight\" title=\"Landed knight\">landed knights</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafcider_hall.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafcider_hall.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-knightly_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-knightly-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Reach.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The Reach and the location of Cider Hall\"><img alt=\"The Reach and the location of Cider Hall\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/300px-The_Reach.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"385\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/450px-The_Reach.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/600px-The_Reach.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 38.9%; left: 63.6%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -6px; top: -6px; width: 12px; font-size: 12px;\"><img alt=\"The Reach and the location of Cider Hall\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Cider Hall\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/18px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/24px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 100%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Cider Hall</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/The_Reach\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Reach\">The Reach</a> and the location of Cider Hall\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Cider_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Owen_Fossoway\" title=\"Owen Fossoway\">Owen Fossoway</a> declared for the <a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">greens</a> at the start of the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>. He was one of the thirteen <a href=\"/index.php/Caltrops\" title=\"Caltrops\">Caltrops</a>, a group of nobles from the reach who conspired against the <a href=\"/index.php/Two_Betrayers\" title=\"Two Betrayers\">Two Betrayers</a>. Lord Owen died in the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Battle_of_Tumbleton\" title=\"Second Battle of Tumbleton\">Second Battle of Tumbleton</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In an unknown time between <a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209&#160;AC</a>, the house lost the lordship.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafcider_hall.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafcider_hall.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-knightly_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-knightly-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Lords_of_Cider_Hall\">Known Lords of Cider Hall</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Cider_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Lords of Cider Hall\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Owen_Fossoway\" title=\"Owen Fossoway\">Owen Fossoway</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Cider_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Princess_and_the_Queen\" title=\"The Princess and the Queen\">The Princess and the Queen</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Overthrown.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafcider_hall.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafcider_hall.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7